From: xuefenghao5121 <xuefenghao5121@users.noreply.github.com>
Date: Wed, 8 Apr 2026 21:11:06 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Phase 5C: BF16 oneDNN integration with direct kernel
 interface
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Add gemm_bf16_bf16bf16f32() driver for native BF16 input
- Add pack_a_bf16_direct/pack_b_bf16_direct for BF16→BF16 packing
- Fix __bf16 vs bfloat16_t type mismatch in NEON/SVE kernels
- Add BF16 microkernel registration with priority-based selection

Performance: ~2x speedup over FP32 GEMM (179 vs 90 GFLOPS on Neoverse N2)

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
